scenes.description: Kiara welcomes Mori Calliope and Gawr Gura as guests and discusses her new 3D model with them.
Kiara begins the 'Kiwawa Quiz' segment, testing Calliope and Gura's knowledge about her.

subtitles.original: Wait a second,
subtitles.english: Wait a second,

subtitles.original: aren't we missing certain Myth members?
subtitles.english: aren't we missing certain Myth members?

subtitles.original: Yes, we are! Of course we are!
subtitles.english: Yes, we are! Of course we are!

subtitles.original: So please come and say hello to Gura and Callie!
subtitles.english: So please come and say hello to Gura and Callie!

subtitles.original: Wee-wee-wee-wee!
subtitles.english: Wee-wee-wee-wee!

subtitles.english: Hello! Hello! Hello! Happy birthday, Kiara!

subtitles.english: Finally, like, I can do my whole, I can show off my body in 3D

subtitles.original: for a whole stream, yeah! It's so detailed and beautiful.
subtitles.english: for a whole stream, yeah! It's so detailed and beautiful.

subtitles.english: Oh, thank you for looking at me. What's your favorite part? Tell me window.

subtitles.original: Uh, I like the bow on the back. Yeah, the bow's cool, right?

subtitles.original: You never get to see that. Yeah, yeah, yeah,

subtitles.english: you can only see that in 3D. Right, and the little wings too, so precious.

subtitles.english: Oh, that's a good question. Well, maybe another time.

subtitles.english: Maybe, maybe at a 3D debut stream, which this is not. Right. Yeah, right, right.

subtitles.english: Alright, well girls, we are the same generation, so one would assume that you know a thing or two about me, right?

subtitles.english: Yeah, of course! We've only met met many times. Yes, especially us, yes, yes.

subtitles.english: I have five questions for you girls. And if you answer at least four of the questions correctly,
